summary:
This is a simple Gold Coin replacer, replaces the vanilla gold coin with a new Celtic one.

Comes with a new Model and a new Texture.
descriptionHtml:
[center][IMG]http://img802.imageshack.us/img802/3448/cointitle.png[/IMG][/center]

=================
Requirements:
=================

Skyrim 1.5.24.0

=================
Description:
=================

This is a simple Gold Coin replacer, replaces the vanilla gold coin with a new Celtic one.

Comes with a new Model and a new Texture. Texture is high resolution (1024x2048) and model is a higher poly than the vanilla model.

=================
Installation
=================

1. Extract this archive to any folder and then copy the contents to Skryim\'s Data
folder.

=================
Un-Installation:
=================

1. Delete the files/folders associated with the mod.

Meshes\\Clutter\\Coin01.nif
Textures\\Clutter\\Coin01.dds
Textures\\Clutter\\Coin01_n.dds
